# Primitive class literals in annotation defaults must render the raw keyword (void.class / int.class /
# boolean.class), never the SafeIdentifier-mangled void_.class / int_.class. Reference types
# (String.class) are unaffected either way. Real hit: fastjson2 @JSONType `builder() default void.class`.
+default void.class
+default int.class
+default boolean.class
+default String.class
-void_.class
-int_.class
-boolean_.class
